title: Seybold SF 2003
content:
Anybody going to [Seybold SF](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317181451/http:/www.seybold365.com/) this year?   
   
I see Thomas Phinney is on the speakers list... I'm also   
speaking on the "stock photography grows up" panel   
alongside Sheldon from Veer. Should be fun.
author: Joe Pemberton
